🚀 Project Idea: Campus-Flow
The Problem: Canteen mein bheed, token ke liye ladaai, aur class se late hona.
The Solution: Ek mobile-friendly web app jahan bacha class se nikalte hi order kare, canteen wale ko ticket mil jaye, aur jab khana ready ho toh bache ke phone par notification aa jaye.
🛠 Tech Stack (Industry Standard - Backend Focused)
Component	Technology	Why it's a "Bhaiya-Level" choice?
Frontend	Next.js 15 (Tailwind + Shadcn/UI)	Mobile-first look deta hai aur fast hai.
Backend	Node.js (Express) + TypeScript	Type safety interview mein bohot badi baat mani jati hai.
Database	PostgreSQL (Supabase)	ACID transactions ke liye best hai (Order miss nahi hona chahiye).
Real-time	Socket.io or Supabase Realtime	Order status Pending se Ready hotey hi screen update hogi.
State/Cart	Zustand	Cart management handle karne ke liye (Jaise FoodBash mein hai).
Payments	Razorpay (Test Mode)	Real-world feel deta hai.
⚙️ Backend Logic (Jo aapko practice karni hai)
Recruiter aapka backend dekh kar impress hoga agar aapne ye 3 cheezein handle ki:
The Order Lifecycle (State Machine):
PLACED -> ACCEPTED -> PREPARING -> READY -> COLLECTED.
Backend logic likhna ki koi status bypass na kar sake.
Concurrency Handling (Inventory Lock):
Problem: Canteen mein 5 Samosas bache hain, lekin 10 bacho ne ek saath "Order" daba diya.
Backend Practice: Database locking seekho taaki inventory minus mein na chali jaye.
The "Token" System:
Har order par ek unique Digital Token (QR code style) generate karna jo student canteen mein dikhayega.
📱 Product-Level Screens (Value Addition)
Student Dashboard: Live menu, live crowd indicator (Canteen mein kitni bheed hai), aur active orders.
Canteen Dashboard (The Real System): Yahan canteen wala bade boxes mein order dekhega aur button dabayega "Food is Ready".
Admin Panel: Price update karna, menu item add/delete karna (Full CRUD practice).
💡 Why is this better than a simple "Food App"?
Daily Use: Bacha har break mein isse use karega.
Solves Human Problem: No more standing in lines.
Real Value: Canteen wale ka hisab-kitab (accounting) asan ho jata hai.
